    "Other attempts were conducted to align LLMs to the medical domain, working on prompting [57] and prompt tuning [58].",
    "Moreover, efforts are currently underway to devise procedures for evaluating bias and harms associated with fairness [59].",
    "Finally, a multidisciplinary team composed of physicians, hospital administrators, lawyers, and AI researchers is working on Hippocratic AI.",
